The paper deals with the problem of taking OLAP analysis to the graph data model, which involves querying multidimensional databases. This suggests that the paper could belong to the database (cs.DB) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. However, the paper specifically focuses on graph analysis, which suggests that it could also belong to the data structures (cs.DS) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a formal multidimensional model for graph analysis, which involves background information in the form of dimension hierarchies, suggesting that it could also belong to the systems and control (cs.SY) or social and information networks (cs.SI) sub-categories.
